                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260406-37-off195 t18260406-37-cd196"></join>, and stealing half a yard of waistcoating, value 2s.; 1 yard of woollen cloth, value 9s.; 1 petticoat, value 1s.; 1 night jacket, value 2s.; 1 yard of stuff, value 1s.; 1 yard of jean, value 6d., and 1 coverlid, value 10s.
