                     <interp inst="t18260406-37-person285" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the 15th of March, I searched the prisoner's house, and found a piece of plaid stuff, a piece of jean, a piece of black calico, and several remnants of white calico; part of them were in a box.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined by Mr. PHILLIPS. Q. These are articles a woman was likely to have? A. Yes. I took him on the 14th.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. My wife bought these things at Spitalfields-market.</p>
